# Metrics Database

This directory stores monthly performance metrics for the team and individual agents.

## Structure

```
metrics/
├── 2026-03.json
├── 2026-04.json
└── ...
```

## Tracked Metrics

### Team Metrics
- Autonomy rate
- Decision accuracy
- Consensus success rate
- Escalation rate
- Average cycle time
- Quality score

### Agent Metrics
- Decisions participated
- Decision accuracy
- Average confidence
- Confidence calibration
- Response time
- Contribution quality

### Patterns
- Successful patterns
- Anti-patterns
- Trends and insights
